@startuml
title FIG-05-01. C4 levels of zoom

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #E8F1FA
  BorderColor #2F5D7C
  FontColor #111111
  RoundCorner 8
}
skinparam arrow {
  Color #555555
  FontColor #333333
}

left to right direction

rectangle "System Context\n\nQuestion:\nWho uses the system,\nand what is around it?" as context
rectangle "Container\n\nQuestion:\nWhat runs or stores data\ninside the system?" as container
rectangle "Component\n\nQuestion:\nWhat major parts sit inside\na container?" as component
rectangle "Code\n\nQuestion:\nWhat classes or code units\nmatter for this design?" as code

context --> container : zoom in
container --> component : zoom in
component --> code : zoom in

note bottom of code
  The code level is optional for many
  architecture discussions.
end note

@enduml
